Name: Zoomoov
text: Zoomoov is a young company operating rides for children in Singapore. Hop onto our safari themed animal rides for a whole day of delight and excitement! Make our outlets your indoor playground and take our ZOOMOOV animals out for a spin!

Name: 328 Katong Laksa
text: For those who love a little heat, 328 Katong Laksa serves up a bowl of spicy broth enriched with creamy coconut milk and the taste of seafood. Pair it with our signature Otak Otak, it will make breaking a sweat worth it!

Name: 85 Redhill Teochew Fishball Noodles
text: 85 Redhill Teochew Fishball Noodles specialises in Teochew Style Fishball Noodles that preserves the nostalgic flavour and taste. Served with a generous portion of Handmade Teochew Fishball and Fishcake that is light and bouncy but dense in flavour, 85 Redhill Teochew Fishball Noodles will keep you hooked!

Name: Adrift Anapauo Massage & Spa
text: Relax your mind and body at Adrift Anapauo with our range of massage services including Foot Reflexology, Body Massages and Aroma Candle Therapy.

Name: AESOP
text: Aesop retails skin, hair and body care products that are formulated using the finest plant-based and laboratory-made ingredients. From cleansers that restore the balance of your skin to treatments that combat ageing, Aesop has the perfect personal care solutions for you.

Name: AIBI
text: Look good and feel great with AIBI! Exercise at the comfort of your own home. AIBI takes on a holistic 3-pronged approach of Health, Beauty and Fitness to achieve quality lifestyle for all individuals at every stage of your life. AIBI constantly brings in the latest and innovative products to improve your exercise experience.

Name: Aimer
text: Aimer sculpts the perfect fit of lingerie catered to Asian females. We consistently focus on creative designs which combine Eastern aesthetics and Western fashion in a perfect harmony. Sticking to our oriental roots, we have also developed lines of classic collections that incorporates traditional Chinese design elements into our lingerie.

Name: Akimitsu
text: Akimitsu is the award-winning Tempura & Tendon restaurant originated from Asakusa, Japan with over 128 years of history. Indulge in golden crispy Tempura Prawns with ba serving of crunchy greens to complete your bowl.

Name: ALDO
text: Aldo specializes in the creation of high-quality fashion footwear and accessories. This sought-after brand pays close attention to detail and to fine craftsmanship. ALDO is dedicated to bringing you both quality and cutting-edge trends at affordable prices, season after season. Whether the latest footwear trends are breaking in London, Milan, Paris, New York or Tokyo, Aldo will have them on your feet first!

Name: Alexandria Maison
text: The Alexandria Maison line features a new collection of beautiful creations; highlighting her commitment to providing modern contemporary, elegant, art-themed, handcrafted pieces that make a statement. Different international designers and brands contributed to these beautiful creations which were made and selected carefully with the discerning, yet budget-minded, fashion-forward person in mind. The creations are appreciated and well received by customers worldwide for its timeless style and elegance.

Name: Aloha Poké
text: Aloha Poké is the first of its kind in Singapore. Staying true to the Hawaiian heritage, their fish is seasoned to perfection, with each bite taking you back to that perfect sunny day on Waikiki Beach. The crisp vegetables will remind you of the refreshing breeze of the Pacific Ocean. Aloha! Poké will keep you grinding (Hawaiian slang for eating like there is no tomorrow) without the guilt factor. Poké (pronounced “Poh-Kay”) is a Hawaiian staple and the choice food of surfers. Traditional Poké comprises of seasoned Ahi (Tuna) tossed with toasted sesame seeds, sweet onions and scallions. It’s great on its own; but for a heartier meal it can be consumed over rice and salad. At Aloha our Poké is always prepared fresh with generous amounts of tuna or salmon lightly marinated in secret sauces and topped off with a wide selection of Add-ons and Superfoods. The secret formula – prepare each bowl with love. Their food is never dressed, even in its purest form, it is stunningly beautiful. Their objective is sweet and simple, to provide a healthy, tasty meal that is made of the highest quality ingredients.Taste the Freshness of Hawaii at Aloha Poké…

Name: Anjappar
text: Preserving the best culinary traditions of Chennai, Anjappar brings hearty North and South Indian cuisine to warm your stomach. With the perfect spice blend and secret home recipes, Anjappar will change your understanding of what is true Indian cuisine.

Name: Aoyama Hair Studio
text: Have your hair pampered by our team of skilled Japanese stylists and highly trained local stylists, bringing you the latest hair trends, most advanced in hair technology and innovative styling techniques straight from Japan. Experience service with a personal touch along with our characteristic hospitality. Aoyama hair studio salon only uses eco-friendly and non-damaging products that are gentle to your hair and helps to bring out its natural texture.

Name: Artary
text: ARTARY Academy of Children's Art. ARTARY’s art experience is uniquely Singaporean, second to none. From admissions to graduation, for both students and parents, experience is at the heart of everything we do. Countless hours have been put into studying, creating, commissioning and refining the many different components that make up the best experience for the thousands of students who have come through our doors.

Name: ASICS
text: Through scientific approaches and collaboration with athletes, Asics creates highly innovative sports product solutions that provide athletes with the most comfortable and performance-enhancing shoes and apparel on the market. Our foot scanning system helps you find your perfect Asics fit.

Name: Aureus Academy
text: Aureus Academy specializes in providing individually tailored piano, violin, guitar, and vocal lessons to students of all ages and abilities. We believe one-on-one is the best environment to learn a musical instrument, but the trick is keeping students engaged while making the lessons fun and rewarding! Our lessons are designed to engage each student in a way that suits their learning style.

Name: A|X Armani Exchange
text: A|X Armani Exchange is inspired by street-chic culture and everything that signifies freedom and personal style. Offering a wide range of stylish pieces from statement outer wears to minimalistic silhouettes featuring denim, our collection combines comfort and style in the urbanites.

Name: BABYSPA
text: Swim well, Grow well. To improve babies' physical growth and mental development in the most critical stage of a child's life, BabySPA carries out its mission through its innovative system of strengthening and stimulating babies using a warm water-based method. Rest assured that our services such as swimming, massage and haircut are carried out by trained staff under a safe environment.

Name: Bank of China
text: With over 70 years of presence in the local banking industry, Bank of China Singapore Branch provides a full range of financial services to its customers from Singapore, China as well as the surrounding region.The main businesses of Bank of China include corporate banking, retail banking, trade financing and international trade settlement, with specialized knowledge and expertise in China-related trade financing and settlements, and remittance services.

Name: Bata
text: Bata carries a wide range of footwear that caters to your every need - from school shoes to sports shoes optimized for the active lifestyle, head over to Bata to find your perfect fit.

Name: Beauty Language
text: Beauty Language is a leading beauty retailer offering a wide selection of the finest fragrance, cosmetics, hair, facial and skin care products in Singapore.

Name: BEGA
text: With intricate attention to details, Bega tailors each silhouette to flatter every body type so that Bega women can confidently flaunt their curves and strut it.

Name: benefit
text: Delivering quick fixes for every gal's peskiest beauty dilemmas and saving eyebrows a pair at a time, Benefit retails brow products and pore correctors amongst other cosmetics that will give you a new look everyday.

Name: Bering
text: BERING blend minimalistic Danish design and optimal material strength effortlessly. High quality materials such as High-Tech-Ceramic, Ultra Light Titanium, Stainless Steel and Sapphire Glass, with their extreme scratch resistance and strength, ensure that time literally leaves no trace.

Name: Better Vision
text: Better Vision holds the firm belief that a healthy eye-sight is essential in living a healthy and well-balanced life. With our extensive experience, we have garnered a distinct advantage in understanding, diagnosing and prescribing appropriate solutions for your eye care needs and requirements. Our broad array of stylish eyewear from celebrated marques, and quality of ophthalmic lenses and contact lenses will definitely give you Better Vision.

Name: BONIA

Be fascinated by our creative designs and intricate craftsmanship which infuses modernism and youthfulness into our timeless creations, offering the leather lovers vogue and contemporary design.

Name: Bowl Thai
text: Bowl Thai offers an enticing quick casual dining destination with an attractive range of well-loved Thai dishes well-suited for diners who are hungry for a taste from the Land of Smiles, backed by a team of experienced chefs, Bowl Thai is set to be an exciting haunt for a comforting taste of Thai cuisine.

Name: Braun Buffel
text: Braun Büffel has built its tradition and reputation over the last century as a designer and producer of top quality leather goods and accessories. Today, it is a premium brand known for exceptional workmanship, superior leather, classic elegance and contemporary appeal. From briefcases to wallets, Braun Buffel produces exquisite leather goods that adds sophistication to your outfit.

Name: BreadTalk Café
text: Perfect for busy professionals and shoppers alike, BreadTalk Cafe makes for a welcoming cosy venue to drop in for a quick breakfast meeting, lunch, leisurely teatime or dinner. Serving all-time comfort food such as Fish & Chips and Mushroom Cabonara, BreadTalk Cafe warms the heart and stomach.

text: Brotzeit is a German Beer Bar and Restaurant offering authentic Bavarian cuisine in a contemporary yet chic setting. Enjoy signature German dishes like the Pork Curry Sausages and Crispy Oven Roasted Pork Knuckles over a chilled glass of beer. Try topping that for a fridate!

Name: Build-A- Bear Workshop
text: The closest thing to your imaginary friend brought to life, create your own fluffy companion at Build-A-Bear Workshop where you can customize everything from the clothes, fur coat and even voice of your plush bear, rabbit, unicorn and more!

Name: Calvin Klein Jeans
text: Since its launch in 1978, Calvin Klein Jeans has been positioned as an authentic designer jeans brand known for its innovative fits, details, and fabrics. Apart from jeans, Calvin Klein Jeans presents a collection of apparel and accessories with a tinge of modern sophistication. Rocking cities worldwide with its ground-breaking advertising campaigns, Calvin Klein Jeans has portrayed itself as an urban and sensual icon. Calvin Klein Jeans will be opening its doors at Westgate in May.

Name: Calvin Klein watches+jewelry

Name: Chrysalis Spa

Name: Citizen
text: CITIZEN WATCH is a true manufacture d'horlogerie with a comprehensive manufacturing process that extends from creating a watch's individual components to its final assembly.  The company operates in more than 100 countries around the world.  Since its founding in 1918, CITIZEN have held the belief of "Better Starts Now" - that is, no matter who you are and what you do, it is always possible to make something better, and now is the time start doing it.Sharing this belief, we have made watches, invented and improved technologies and explored the future of watches such as our proprietary light-powered Eco-Drive technology, and satellite-synchronised timekeeping system Satellite Wave.

Name: Coco & Frank
text: A new confectionery brand that offers premium natural oatmeal and eggless butter cookies. Perfect for pampering yourself and gifting your loved ones.

Name: CoCo ICHIBANYA

Name: Crystal Jade Kitchen

Name: Curry Times

Name: D&C - Design & Comfort

Name: Daniel Wellington
text:
The Swedish brand, Daniel Wellington, founded in 2011,
has quickly established itself as one of the most leading brands in the
industry. The brand has taken the world of watches by storm and is best known
for their classic and minimalistic watches with interchangeable straps.

Name: DBS Bank

Our philosophy is to deliver value at affordable cost to cover customer's needs through their lives. Products and services offered through our branches include credit cards, loans, investment & unit trusts and insurance.

Name: dENiZEN
text: dENiZEN™ was created by original jeans maker Levi Strauss & Co in 2010. With years of American craft and expertise, the brand focuses on outfitting a new generation with a legacy of its well-crafted functional jeanswear and contemporary fashion essentials. dENiZEN™ endeavours to advocate confidence, inspiration and self expression through its iconic denim pieces and trend-led seasonal hues.

Name: Desigual
text: Desigual's colorful printed pieces stands out from your typical monochromatic silhouettes by injecting some vibrancy into your wardrobe and your day. With a wide selection of apparels for men, women and children, pick an outfit that will lift your mood!

With our experienced audiologists, audiometrists and hearing care consultants, we provide free hearing screen and consultations as well. We carry the full product range of leading hearing aid brands at competitive prices.

We provide sincere care and thorough counselling and offering the safest and most appropriate type of treatment best suited to each patient's needs.

Name: EC House

Name: ECCO

With a keen eye for the hottest runway trends, we incorporate these fast fashion inspirations into stylish footwear for the gents and the ladies.

Name: ESINEY
text: Esiney shop sells fashionable and affordable mobile accessories such as handphone casing, screen protector, portable charger and more.

Name: Estetica

With more than 30 years of experience, Estetica is known for its quality service, as well as its custom designed treatment bed layered with NASA developed memory foam, beauty treatments and products based on Nobel prize Winning research and its proprietary massage techniques.

Name: Eureka Snack Bar
text: Snack time is always enjoying, so we like to implement some into the snack and make it stress free while having snack by taking your health into consideration on our product line.  We understand that almost everyone love snack, from school kids to elderly, thus our snack variety are plenty and refreshing every year.We like to see everyone around us live a happy and healthy life, thus we start it with our own self, we smile, we greet, we listen and we care about everyone we meet in our everyday life, believing that what we do will make your day better and happier.  Our ranges of customer are wide, from school kids to elderly, because everyone should not miss the fun of having snack.Popcorns are always our main product which we are so proud of it since our popcorn not only comes with variety of flavours, it also come in round shape that makes it coated evenly with your favourite seasoning, all thanks to the special "mushroom" popcorn maize, we are able to make our popcorn tastier and crunchier.  Moreover, we only use non GMO popcorn maize and natural fine ingredient to "pop" this extraordinary snack and bring fun to kill your bore moment.

Name: excluniqueeee
text: Welcome to excluniqueeee!Westies we are here for you! Here at excluniqueeee, we have even more to offer you. As always, our eclectic curation of jewelleries, apparels and locally crafted goods are here to pamper you. Don't miss out on trendy designs and exclusive pieces.A weekend shopping can now be a regular quick departure from the stressful day at work. There are so much to discover here. Selection of jewelleries vary from statement pieces for the glamorous night out, hippy styles for the bohemian soul, minimalistic designs for modern individual, quirky motif that suits the peculiar nature and timeless jewellery catering to silver lover.We also have in store compilation of Japanese canvas sling bags with exclusive hand-drawn motif by local artist, Band of Doodle. Because at excluniqueeee we have a whimsical section, with chock-full of plush toys. Fayy terranium are a great gift to teach your kids about nature & nurture. Now they can own a portable green sanctuary while promoting a greener environment to everyone.Eccentric goods all under one roof, for the young at hearts and inquiring of minds.

Name: Expert Beaute
text: Expert Beaute specializes in all things beauty, from eyebrow embroidery to express gelish manicure. Pamper yourself at Expert Beaute!

Name: FANCL
text: Founded in Japan in 1980, FANCL has since inception devoted its resources to innovating “PRESERVATIVE-FREE” products. The brand’s holistic beauty approach underlines its purpose to drive skin and body wellness without the use of preservatives in its products. Today, FANCL has built an extensive R&D laboratory in Japan with resources dedicated to innovation, product development and skin research. All facets of the brand are aligned to spread its promise of delivering products free from preservatives.

Name: Fish & Co.

From shellfishes to crustaceans and squids, you name it, we've got it! If Mediterrenean South Africa is insufficient for that appetite, travel around the world with us and try out one of our six interpretations of Fish & Chips from around the world.

Name: Fitness First Platinum

For the hardcore gym junkies, get working at our state of the art gyms staffed with experienced trainers to help you achieve your fitness goals.

Name: Flaming Queen
text: In March 2010, Accendo Asia acquired Flaming Queen, a high end home fragrance retailer located in Mandarin Gallery. Flaming Queen has grown into a multi-brand retailer and distributor of several reputable and premium room fragrance brands. Flaming Queen has its own brand of high quality essential oil, massage oil and plans are underway to increase the product range.

Name: Food Republic
text: Food Republic introduces the best local hawker fare and street food under one roof. From must-eats wok signatures like Hokkien Prawn Mee to hand-tossed Roti Prata, Food Republic showcases the best culinary traditions of our cultural melting pot.

Name: FotoHub
text: Whether you want to commemorate a special event, leave an impression or preserve your memories for years to come, you will find the right solution at FotoHub where we provide printing and collaging services that help you to document every picture worthy moment.

Name: Gen

Name: Giordano Ladies
text: Giordano Ladies retails womenswear that echoes their pursuit of simplicity. With an unwavering commitment to providing simple, clean lines, quality workmanship, and attentive customer service, Giordano Ladies has built a strong loyal following throughout the world.

Name: Godiva Belgium 1926

Name: Gong Cha
text: The essence of Gong Cha, or Tribute Tea, originated from the provision of the most premium and refined teas to the Emperor of China. It represents the highest quality and expectations of beverages. Established in Taiwan in 2006, Gong Cha has become deeply appreciated by its customers, gaining global renown by word of mouth and a uniquely customised service.Today, Gong Cha outlets around the world number near 1,500, having become a widespread sensational concept among various consumers. Gong Cha’s story is one that roots itself as one of the most reliable providers of quality tea in the world.

Name: Gong Yuan Ma La Tang
text: At Gong Yuan Ma La Tang, Soup Matters.The team loves it when you leave our bowls ‘cleaned’. More than just soups, you can actually drink the Ma La!How to order?Choose the ingredients from the variety of choices Choose your soup base (Ma La, Pork Broth, Pickled Vegetables). It is recommended to fill half your bowl with vegetables as this will optimise the soup taste and bring out the flavours. Enjoy your soup!

Name: Greendot
text: Greendot serves up meat-free dishes carefully designed by our nutritionists to meet your dietary needs. Try out our meatless interpretation of the Tom Yum Noodles and Shiitake Mushroom Laksa and see if you can notice the difference! Greendot makes going meatless a breeze by replacing them with nutri-packed greens and plant-based proteins.

Name: Guardian

Carrying a range of health care, skin care and beauty products, and our in-store specialists offer customers expert advice and support. We also provide professional services such as patient-care counselling and dispensary services at our pharmacies.

Name: Ha Jun
text: Halal certified restaurant serving assortment of Korean dishes.

Our dental clini provides general dentistry, restorative dentistry and cosmetic dentistry services.

Name: Honolulu Café
text: Founded in 1940s by the late Mr Yeung Jin Hei, Hong Kong’s treasured café, Honolulu Café also fondly known by locals as ‘Cha Chaan Teng’.Well-known for its flaky pastry and soft egg custard center, Honolulu Café’s egg tarts utilises a time-tested method by freezing the dough overnight to fold 192 layers for a crispy and flaky shell. The egg tarts are baked daily to ensure freshness.Besides the famous Egg Tarts and Hong Kong Milk Tea, Honolulu Café has also selected many popular items from its existing Hong Kong menu to provide diners with a more authentic Cha Chaan Teng experience. To ensure that the well-loved taste of Honolulu Café remains as similar as possible, the Singapore kitchen in Honolulu Café’s will be helmed by carefully selected chefs from Hong Kong’s Honolulu Café.

Name: Hot Tomato Café & Grill
text: From all-time western favorites like Rib Eye Steak to Chargrilled Specialties on the carving board like the Fillet Mignon & Grilled Garlic Shrimp, enjoy quality cuts at affordable prices here at Hot Tomato Café & Grill.

Name: Häagen-Dazs
text: Häagen-Dazs ice cream starts with real cream and milk, blended with carefully selected ingredients, to create an ice cream with a unique velvety texture and unforgettable taste. Every mouthful of Häagen-Dazs is an absorbing, intensely pleasurable experience. Try out favorites like Rum Raisin, Macadamia Nut and Banana Chocolate Brownie.

Name: Inforcom

Name: Irvins Salted Egg

Name: Kushiya

text: L'OCCITANE offers a provencal lifestyle of natural beauty, colors, scents and traditions. Using only 100% natural essential oils and ingredients with respect to man and the environment, the highest quality skincare, body care and fragrances are created.

Its signature cake Lady M Mille Crêpes features twenty paper-thin handmade crêpes layered with light pastries cream topped with a nutty golden caramel.

Name: Lampe Berger Paris
text: Freshen up any room you are in with fragrances from Lampe Berger!

Name: LANEIGE
text: Achieve naturally hydrated and supple skin anytime, anywhere with Laneige. Using our Skin Veil Base Cushion that gives you a radiant and even skin tone, be assured your skin is always camera ready!

text: Epitex provides quality bed linen that promotes a good night's rest. Our linens are made from natural fibres extracted from bamboo or cotton so you can rest on the softest linens and nestle into sleep.

text: At Long John Silver's, our secret batter, prepared fresh throughout the day, distinguishes our deep fried gems from the sea from other fishes out there. Whether you are looking for great fish, seafood and chicken at an affordable price, or a perfect place to dine with your family and friends, Long John Silver's has something for everyone.

Name: Lovey
text: Lovey carries a range of female apparels such as dresses and bottoms that are perfect for a casual sundate in this tropical heat.

Name: MAC WIN
text: Mac Win provides repair and trade in services for IT devices and also retails accessories.

Name: Masizzim
text: An amalgamation of the Korean words ‘masi’ (delicious) and ‘jjim’ (steam), Masizzim (pronounced ma-see-zim) distinguishes itself from all other Korean eateries with their famous 'Galbi Jjim', beef and pork stew dishes. These are complemented by a supporting cast of scrumptious side dishes, such as mix grain Rice Balls, Egg Rolls and three types of savoury Pancakes.

Name: Men Don Tei
text: At Men Don Tei, we serve ramen so good we will have you slurping them up in no time! Beyond a savoury bowl of umami, our extensive menu includes Ebitama Udon with ebi tempura and egg, and Kaisen Bara Chirashi which features a generous assortment of fresh sashimi topped on vinegary sushi rice. For those constantly on the go, we have a takeout counter for picking up fresh sushi.

Name: Menya Musashi
text: Menya Musashi offers noodles in a variety of different textures and a selection of soup base including white, red and black soup options. Head over and be pampered with a selection of signature broths such as their Signature White Tonkotsu, the Triple soup for chicken lovers and Tokyo-Ueno style soup which features the flavors of the sea.

Name: Miam Miam
text: Combining the culinary creations from the east and the West, Miam Miam dishes up French-Japanese fusion creations that will steal your heart. From the decadent Lobster Bisque Spaghetti to the fluffy Matcha Souffle Pancakes for your after meal treat, indulge in the best of both worlds!

Name: Mindchamps Reading & Writing
text: At MindChamps Reading & Writing, we build your child's love for stories so that by the age of seven, they will be equipped to become active and skilled readers and writers FOR LIFE!

Name: Miniso
text: Established in Tokyo, Miniso was jointly founded with the aim of advocating a fashionable and relaxed lifestyle. Today, Miniso is a global fast fashion designer brand, offering a wide range of products across 10 product categories including lifestyle, home, gifts, and electronics. Miniso is dedicated to providing customers with quality and creative products at affordable prices; Miniso products are priced from as low as $3.

Name: Mirage Aesthetic

Mirage Aesthetic uses a combination of the latest non-invasive aesthetic technology and specialized skincare products from Korea to customize the perfect solution for your skin type.

Name: MISSHA
text: MISSHA is the top selling brand of cosmetic in Korea and has received international recognition for its high standard of quality skincare and cosmetic products. Main ingredients used are natural plant extract which has passed the strictest care standards. From tightening masks to pore cleansers, we have the solution to your skincare woes.

Name: MISTER MINIT
text: Mister Minit specializes in repair services, key fitting and duplication. We also provide engraving services and carry leather care products.

Name: Monica Vinader
text: Monica Vinader is a British luxury jewellery brand that celebrates individuality. Opening up a new category between fashion and fine jewellery, MV creates instantly wearable, contemporary pieces to style, stack and personalise with engraving.Monica's unique designs have a diverse celebrity following including Emma Watson, Olivia Palermo and the Duchess of Cambridge. Our iconic friendship bracelets, vibrant gemstones and cutting-edge diamond pieces have made Monica Vinader internationally successful.At our debut in 2008, Monica Vinader won Brand of the Year at the UK Jewellery Awards, and has since been stocked by global luxury retailers including Harrods, Selfridges, Liberty, Net-A-Porter and Boutique 1. You can step into the world of Monica Vinader at our boutiques in London's Chelsea, Mayfair and Canary Wharf, and in Hong Kong's ifc Mall.

Name: Mugiya
text: Mugiya is a bakery that specialises in creating unforgettable memories for your tastebuds. Simply said, we love bread. It is something you will be able to tell once you put it in your mouth. Every bread is made with precision and enjoyment.We started out humbly from a small shop at Kitchener Road, and right now we have open up several outlets.

Name: Musee Platinum Tokyo
text: MUSEE offers the hair removal services that will get you out of any unwanted hairy situations, leaving you with smooth soft skin. Never have to worry about forgetting to shave for that sleeveless top anymore!

Name: My First Skool

At My First Skool, they provide a rich learning environment and a range of activities that facilitate optimal growth and development of your child.

Name: My Gym
text: Adopting the holistic approach to education, My Gym focuses on honing the creative side of your child. With programmes such as Dance, Music and Art, My Gym develops the aesthetic talents in your young ones.

text: N20 Nail Spa provides premier nail care manicure and pedicure services in Singapore. Head down to N20 Nail Spa and pamper your nails with a new color today.

Name: Naiise
text: Naiise strives to make good design accessible by retailing novelty items and unique designs and working closely with its community curators and designers to continually source for products that will add some quirkiness and individualism to your space.

Name: New York Skin Solutions

Visit us for financial advice or your policy servicing needs in areas such as the renewal or endorsements for policies regarding accidents, travel, life policies and more.

text: NYX / NIKS / noun - (Greek Mythology) Goddess of the Night—she is a symbol of beauty, power and creative inspiration.WHO WE ARE + WHAT WE DO: PROFESSIONAL MAKEUP FOR ALLNYX Professional Makeup offers the most complete line of affordable professional makeup to a global community of digitally savvy makeup lovers. Our products are always based on real-time trends and deliver on the richest color offering and quality. Our mission is to enable, empower and educate all makeup enthusiasts to become their very own makeup artist. We celebrate makeup artistry and creativity in everyone.

Name: Oh My
text: Instagram this: refreshing tropical lemonade in lightbulb bottles that actually lights up and artisanal Hummingbird cake infused with banana, pineapple and spices. Try finding this anywhere else other than Oh My Café.

text: Improvised with a healthier and non-oily recipe, try out our specialty Dry Bak Kut Teh, unique to Old Street. For the old-school lovers, indulge in our Premium Loin Ribs soup and be spoilt for over 10 selections of sides including all-time favorites, BraisedPeanuts and Preserved Vegetables.

text: A renowned traditional delicacy. Let's support the only genuine and authentic Original Cake from Danshui, Taiwan in Singapore!

text: Oro Gold is an anti-aging cosmetics line that restores the youthful appearance of the skin due to sun damage, aging and other environmental factors. Our various OROGOLD collections are made with real 24 karat gold imported straight from Italy to the United States and then manufactured in our lab.

text: Owndays retails eyewear that are designed and manufactured inhouse. Capped at a price of just $198, our glasses are fitted with high index aspheric lenses at no additional cost!

text: Delicately hand crafted to the finest quality, PANDORA provides the perfect adornment for every mood and occasion. From necklace statement pieces to the subtle sparkle of delicate bracelets, walk into every room with understated beauty.

Serving up a vibrant mix of Vietnamese delights from different regions in Vietnam as well as the healthy and tasty nature of Vietnamese fare, diners can indulge in our signature Beef and Chicken Pho, with the flavorsome stock promising to wet your taste buds. Pho Street also offers a wide variety of street snacks which includes the famous Summer Roll and Crispy Fried Pork Roll.

Be it classical Iyengar Yoga, Ashtanga Yoga or Flow Yoga including specialized classes in Prenatal, Aerial Yoga, Yin Yoga Rehabilitative, Yoga for Kids or Power Yoga – you’ll definitely find a comprehensive list of classes that will rejuvenate you at our studios.

Name: Superga
text:
Born 1911 in Torino, Italy, under the stewardship of Walter Martiny,
Superga started producing shoes with vulcanized rubber soles, ensuring both flexibility
and durability, thereby redefining the humble trainer. The Classic Superga 2750
range has been an icon from the beginning. Long a favourite for taking Italians
from the city to the beach during the weekends, its ubiquity demonstrates its
versatility, and crucially, comfort— thus the slogan “People’s shoes of Italy”.

Name: Sushi Express
text: Sushi Express is fast becoming the most recognisable name for sushi in Asia, serving fresh, delicious sushi at an affordable price. With more than 60 varieties within your immediate reach, everything @ $1.5++/plate. What are you waiting for? So drop by, relax and enjoy!

Name: Yoogane
text: Wildly popular and arguably one of the best in Korea, Yoogane brings the Korean heat into Signapore. Well-loved for our unique blend of sauces and seasoning that marinates our chicken to a spicy tangy perfection, try out our signature Yoogane's Chicken Galbi - a generous portion of flavorful spicy chicken stir fried with an assortment of greens and rice cake to balance the heat.

Name: Yves Rocher
text: With bodycare and skincare products made from natural botanical ingredients, Yves Rocher creates a series of beauty products that can combat aging and wrinkling of different skin types and hydrate your skin to return the suppleness to your complexion.

Name: Zaffron Kitchen
text: Voted 'Best Indian Restaurant 2013' and gaining numerous rave reviews from the media, Zaffron Kitchen serves an excellent mix of North, South and local Indian favourites. Whether you are a gourmet of Indian food or an inquisitive diner who is looking for a place to chill and enjoy good food, get ready for a gastronomic exploration that will bring your dining experience to a whole new level.

Name: Zoomoov
text: Zoomoov is a young company operating rides for children in Singapore. Hop onto our safari themed animal rides for a whole day of delight and excitement! Make our outlets your indoor playground and take our ZOOMOOV animals out for a spin!
